<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ttikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kulacekara tevaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="20">2 <g type="numeral">10</g></num> Āvatu tu <gap reason="lost" quantity="13" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ḻamaiyum peṟṟa Uttirāṭattu nāḷ <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaṅkoṇṭa <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> vūr nāṭṭu tiruviṭavantai nācciyārku <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> muṭaiyāṉ Olai tiruviṭavantai Ūṟk kaṉak <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> varākapaṭṭaṉ kāṇi Āyira muḷḷikkuṭaiyārāka <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ṟku tirunāmattukkāṇi Āka viṭṭa nila mūṉṟu veliyu <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> nam Innilattāl vanta kaṭamai Āyam kācukaṭa <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
