<p>II Piece</p>

<p>
<lb n="10"/>nāḷ Oṉṟukku Amutupaṭikku Arici patakkum kaṟiamutu
<lb n="11"/>miḷakamutu Āḻākkum tayiramutu nāḻikkum Ilaiyamutu
<lb n="12"/>Ippaṭiye Amutu ceyvipārkaḷākavum Amu<unclear>tu</unclear>cey<unclear>p</unclear>
<lb n="13"/>vāṟkku pi<unclear>ra</unclear>cātam Aṟunāḻiyum tirumaññaṉam Eṭuppā
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ril tirunantavaṉañ ceyum <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kākaṟ pi<unclear>ra</unclear>cātam nāna
<lb n="15" break="no"/>pi<supplied reason="omitted">ra</supplied>cātam Aññāḻiyum Ākap piracātam pākkum naṭa
